
OLConf (OpenbLdConf) is a shared library based on yamlgen, providing builders and 
runners specific to OpenBLDC. 
These are: 

- RegisterConfigBuilder and -Runners
- FlagConfigBuilder and -Runners
- DefineConfigBuilder and -Runners

Run `make` to generate 

- The shared library libolconf (olconf/lib/libolconf.so)
- The command line tool olconfgen (olconf/bin/olconfgen)

